WEBVTT

00:01.823 --> 00:03.414
I really don't want anybody to know...

00:03.439 --> 00:05.667
about Jacob or that
I was in the hospital.

00:06.219 --> 00:09.580
Will you promise me that if
you ever feel suicidal again,

00:09.605 --> 00:11.433
that you... you'll just come to me.

00:11.983 --> 00:14.219
I haven't exactly
broken up with Jeff yet.

00:14.244 --> 00:15.469
What if you get him to dump you?

00:15.493 --> 00:17.777
Just tell him that you don't
want to move back to Wisconsin.

00:17.801 --> 00:18.812
I'll move to LA.

00:18.837 --> 00:20.414
But you love Fitchburg.

00:20.618 --> 00:22.101
I love you more.

00:23.522 --> 00:24.771
Can I stay with you tonight?

00:24.796 --> 00:25.971
Yeah.

00:26.174 --> 00:27.769
I think we should implement a rule

00:27.793 --> 00:30.035
that supervisors cannot date anyone

00:30.060 --> 00:31.143
who works under them.

00:31.168 --> 00:32.183
Agreed.

00:32.209 --> 00:33.992
