00:34.017 --> 00:36.536
The app literally doubled the donations!

00:36.561 --> 00:38.721
We only made $10,000, not 20.

00:39.084 --> 00:41.193
- I met my father.
- How'd that go?

00:41.218 --> 00:42.898
We always thought that
he just up and left.

00:42.923 --> 00:44.856
My mom never said
anything good about him.

00:44.881 --> 00:46.414
Is everything okay?

00:46.439 --> 00:47.599
