outstanding rent owed

02:02.270 --> 02:03.510
or where to make payment.

02:04.206 --> 02:05.367
Where did you go to school?

02:05.392 --> 02:06.453
UCSD.

02:06.478 --> 02:08.078
- Legal studies?
- Law.

02:08.634 --> 02:09.817
You're a lawyer?

02:09.842 --> 02:10.842
Yes.

02:11.190 --> 02:12.651
I haven't passed the bar yet.

02:12.676 --> 02:14.168
Well, aren't you a little overqualified

02:14.192 --> 02:15.272
to be a research assistant?

02:16.516 --> 02:17.516
I need a job.

02:18.506 --> 02:21.799
Hm. Well, don't be tempted
to give legal advice.

02:22.353 --> 02:24.473
Oh, don't worry. I will stay in my lane.

02:26.943 --> 02:29.063
All right, back to work.

02:31.000 --> 02:37.074
