02:40.533 --> 02:43.636
How about one that's a little l-less...

02:43.661 --> 02:44.661
Less?

02:44.826 --> 02:46.818
More... relaxed.

02:47.522 --> 02:48.854
Okay.

02:48.879 --> 02:50.031
- You ready?
- Yeah.

02:50.056 --> 02:51.866
What are you doing?
That is a terrible...

02:51.891 --> 02:53.229
- You're a fierce tiger.
- What are you do...

02:53.253 --> 02:54.893
- Please get up.
- You're a Komodo dragon.

03:02.345 --> 03:04.168
And I need a photographer, not a critic.

03:04.193 --> 03:05.262
Well, I'm not a photographer.

03:05.286 --> 03:07.169
Yeah, but you're tall, and
pictures look better from above.

03:07.193 --> 03:08.275
Come on. Let me see.

03:12.418 --> 03:13.826
I like that one.

03:13.851 --> 03:14.851
Ugh. No.

03:15.555 --> 03:17.606
Who invited the dinner
rolls to the party?

03:17.631 --> 03:18.631
You look like you.

03:19.409 --> 03:20.409
Thanks a lot.

03:21.266 --> 03:23.332
Beautiful. And real.

03:24.267 --> 03:26.304
Well, I appreciate the "beautiful" part,

03:26.756 --> 03:29.824
but no one wants to see anything
on Instagram that's too "real".

03:30.191 --> 03:31.391
Oh, this is the one.

03:33.402 --> 03:35.495
I thought the point of the
whole body-positive movement

03:35.519 --> 03:38.770
was to love your real
body, without filters.

03:38.795 --> 03:40.515
Okay, everyone uses filters.

03:40.951 --> 03:43.151
And I'm not trimming or slimming.

03:43.176 --> 03:45.628
Oh, speaking of which,
my mom's gonna be in town

03:45.653 --> 03:47.533
getting one of her "procedures".

03:48.829 --> 03:50.549
At least she's staying
in a hotel this time.

03:53.496 --> 03:55.404
You do remember my mom?

03:55.429 --> 03:56.549
Yeah.

03:56.574 --> 03:57.599
Why?

03:57.789 --> 04:00.109
No reason, you were just
pretty wasted last time.

