Doctor Levin has a payment plan.

05:13.821 --> 05:15.411
Mm-hmm? And what's the interest rate

05:15.427 --> 05:16.577
on this payment plan?

05:16.602 --> 05:17.968
Less than my credit card.

05:17.993 --> 05:21.033
And I would appreciate
a little support, Davia.

05:22.786 --> 05:24.786
Mom, you're a beautiful woman.

05:25.798 --> 05:27.051
I'm over 40,

05:27.208 --> 05:29.528
and single, with no
one to take care of me.

05:30.006 --> 05:31.806
Time's running out, okay?

05:32.069 --> 05:34.249
What, you want me to
end up old and alone?

05:35.423 --> 05:37.603
Mom, you're not gonna end up alone.

05:39.154 --> 05:40.434
You'll always have me.

05:40.946 --> 05:43.806
I know. And I love you so much.

05:44.156 --> 05:45.696
But I can't have sex with you.

05:48.054 --> 05:50.664
Don't you want to find someone

05:50.689 --> 05:52.287
who loves you for what's inside?

05:53.411 --> 05:55.196
Honey, men aren't
interested in the inside

05:55.221 --> 05:57.661
if what's on the outside
doesn't give them a boner.

05:58.191 --> 05:59.951
I got you something.

06:01.025 --> 06:02.774
For my baby girl.

06:02.799 --> 06:04.156
Mm-hmm.

06:04.181 --> 06:05.701
Do you like it?

06:05.931 --> 06:07.714
- It's beautiful.
- Mm-hmm.

06:08.157 --> 06:10.499
And... expensive.

06:10.524 --> 06:11.724
You're welcome.

06:13.914 --> 06:14.955
Thank you.

06:17.256 --> 06:19.501
Oh, my goodness. You are so pretty.

06:19.526 --> 06:20.926
Oh!

06:20.951 --> 06:22.551
And talented.

06:22.971 --> 06:24.696
Look at that gorgeous face.

06:24.721 --> 06:25.855
Mm.

06:25.987 --> 06:28.103
If you just lost 30 pounds,

06:28.128 --> 06:30.212
you could get any man you want.

06:30.237 --> 06:31.237
Muah.

06:39.151 --> 06:42.103
There she is. Congratulations.

06:42.128 --> 06:45.140
- You did it, girl!
- And she raised $20,000.

06:45.165 --> 06:47.568
- You made us proud.
- Her app is genius.

06:47.593 --> 06:48.859
Thank you, all.

06:48.884 --> 06:50.093
So, are you excited?

06:50.118 --> 06:51.961
We heard Evan was there.
He must be impressed.

06:56.672 --> 06:58.533
I think I'm just gonna
tell Evan what happened

06:58.558 --> 07:00.704
and have him garnish my wages,
so no one needs to know.

07:00.728 --> 07:01.768
Whoa, wait.

07:02.393 --> 07:04.020
You don't have to make up that money.

07:04.045 --> 07:07.229
The Center for Transgender
Veterans is expecting $20,000.

07:07.254 --> 07:08.579
They were expecting half that.

07:08.604 --> 07:09.652
They'll understand.

07:09.677 --> 07:11.397
Yeah, well, what about everyone else?

07:11.422 --> 07:13.755
It's a beta test. Things
are supposed to go wrong.

07:13.780 --> 07:15.246
Okay. No, not on my watch.

07:15.504 --> 07:18.839
I mean, all of those guys
are expecting me to fail.

07:18.864 --> 07:20.404
And Evan stood up to
his board of directors.

07:20.416 --> 07:22.044
I can't let him lose his faith in me.

07:22.069 --> 07:24.549
I don't think you have to worry
about Evan losing faith in you.

07:25.903 --> 07:27.963
Oh, my god. Do you still
think that he's doing

07:27.988 --> 07:30.208
- all of this because...
- No, I didn't say that.

07:30.225 --> 07:32.194
- Well, that's what you're implying.
- No, it's not.

07:32.205 --> 07:33.839
Look, I can't talk about this right now.

07:33.863 --> 07:36.643
I don't have time for this. I have
to go down to the art department,

07:36.668 --> 07:38.428
and then I have a
stupid grievance meeting.

07:47.868 --> 07:49.868
_

