28:43.680 --> 28:46.000
Well, I'm watching my figure.

28:46.232 --> 28:48.067
Well, you're too skinny, if you ask me.

28:48.331 --> 28:50.411
And let's have some of those
sweet potato fries, too.

28:50.553 --> 28:51.553
Thank you.

28:52.534 --> 28:53.534
Hey, y'all.

28:55.154 --> 28:57.687
Oh, hey. Uh, you remember my mother?

28:59.053 --> 29:00.773
