- Hi.

29:02.163 --> 29:03.403
But who's this guy?

29:06.194 --> 29:07.434
Where you been?

29:08.922 --> 29:09.922
Around.

29:11.604 --> 29:12.787
Mm.

29:12.812 --> 29:14.771
Well, I'll have the waiter bring out

29:14.796 --> 29:16.890
an order of those
fried artichokes on me.

29:17.163 --> 29:18.499
I know how much you love them.

29:21.868 --> 29:22.868
Mm.

29:30.000 --> 29:31.000
Hey.

29:31.255 --> 29:32.255
Hey.

29:34.353 --> 29:35.353
How'd it go?

29:36.832 --> 29:37.832
