30:07.368 --> 30:08.851
He is a grown-ass man.

30:09.039 --> 30:10.434
He has been taking care of himself

30:10.459 --> 30:11.878
long before you were in the picture.

30:11.902 --> 30:13.362
I understand you want a
relationship with him, but...

30:13.386 --> 30:14.892
