30:43.045 --> 30:45.470
Oh, I'm not really on
social media these days.

30:45.495 --> 30:46.682
No, no, no. I'm good. I'm good.

30:46.706 --> 30:48.209
Come on, you love these.

30:48.717 --> 30:50.417
Oh. Bonnie?

30:50.798 --> 30:51.998
Help me out with these.

30:53.008 --> 30:54.266
