Go away!

33:31.443 --> 33:33.493
- I said, "Go away".
- Well, if you really wanted me to go away,

33:33.517 --> 33:35.629
- you would've locked the door.
- Oh, don't flatter yourself.

33:35.653 --> 33:36.653
I never lock my door.

33:37.734 --> 33:38.974
I'll go away,

33:39.579 --> 33:41.979
if you tell me who you're
mad at. Me or your mom?

33:42.560 --> 33:45.580
Both. I told you I don't
eat in front of my mother.

33:45.764 --> 33:48.798
And that's messed up. Uh,
you, you should be yourself.

33:49.280 --> 33:51.080
That is not for you to decide.

33:51.506 --> 33:52.681
Or to judge.

33:52.706 --> 33:54.417
Especially when you go around hiding

33:54.429 --> 33:55.869
who you are all the time.

33:57.916 --> 33:59.777
You don't get to tell
me to keep your secrets

33:59.802 --> 34:01.813
and then force me into
some sort of confrontation

34:01.838 --> 34:03.078
with my mother.

34:04.179 --> 34:05.739
I mean, look at me, Dennis.

34:08.110 --> 34:09.911
She knows I actually eat.

34:13.808 --> 34:15.860
I don't want to be
myself around my mother

34:15.885 --> 34:17.085
because it hurts.

34:20.259 --> 34:21.498
I'm sorry.

34:23.034 --> 34:24.674
It's just, I care about you,

34:24.699 --> 34:26.460
and she's got no right to judge.

34:26.485 --> 34:27.810
Oh.

34:27.828 --> 34:29.148
You think I don't know that?

34:31.248 --> 34:33.967
You think I, I don't
wish that she could just...

34:34.545 --> 34:35.746
see me...

34:37.250 --> 34:41.335
and not how I look or what I eat?

34:42.550 --> 34:44.951
She's the most insecure,

34:44.976 --> 34:47.243
self-loathing person I've ever known,

34:47.268 --> 34:50.108
and she's projected
that on me my whole life.

34:51.415 --> 34:53.255
Which is why I became anorexic.

34:53.853 --> 34:56.674
And by the way, you can be too skinny.

34:56.954 --> 34:58.554
Okay, I was 90 pounds.

34:59.651 --> 35:01.134
I had to go into a hospital,

35:01.159 --> 35:03.059
get fed with a tube.

35:05.657 --> 35:07.237
I don't want to tell my mom

35:07.823 --> 35:09.623
what I really think about her,

35:10.381 --> 35:12.141
'cause it will only hurt her.

35:15.825 --> 35:17.519
I don't want to make her feel

35:17.544 --> 35:19.124
how she makes me feel.

35:22.561 --> 35:23.561
Oh, hey.

35:48.554 --> 35:49.794
I am sorry.

35:52.057 --> 35:53.057
I know.

35:55.477 --> 35:56.477
It's okay.

36:41.455 --> 36:43.335
You know, she's bound to overstep again,

36:43.359 --> 36:44.783
not to mention she's entitled.

36:45.000 --> 36:47.030
She's young and
determined to change the world,

36:47.054 --> 36:49.230
the way we all were out of law school.

36:49.255 --> 36:51.765
We could use some wide-eyed
energy around here.

36:51.790 --> 36:54.050
There's a difference between
passion and impertinence.

36:54.075 --> 36:55.975
Jeez, you've got it in for her.

36:56.000 --> 36:57.761
No, I have more cases than I can handle,

36:57.786 --> 36:59.381
and I don't have time to rein in the ego

36:59.405 --> 37:01.872
of a young lawyer who's
got something to prove

37:01.897 --> 37:03.057
because she failed the bar.

37:03.571 --> 37:05.815
Don't worry. She's not your problem.

37:05.840 --> 37:07.040
I'll mentor her.

37:07.975 --> 37:08.975
Like you mentored me?

37:10.201 --> 37:11.501
Let's not go there.

37:24.303 --> 37:25.303
Hey, Evan.

37:25.796 --> 37:26.796
Mariana.

37:29.760 --> 37:31.980
Thanks again for everything.

37:32.372 --> 37:33.372
Of course.

37:41.458 --> 37:44.219
So, I was wondering if you would
like to get a drink with me sometime.

37:47.892 --> 37:50.909
To... talk next steps on the app.

37:54.930 --> 37:56.488
Yeah, sure.

37:56.513 --> 37:57.673
When?

38:00.452 --> 38:01.612
How about now?

38:02.194 --> 38:03.194
Now?

38:03.406 --> 38:04.486
Unless you have plans.

38:05.842 --> 38:08.450
Uh, yeah. Now is great.

38:27.364 --> 38:28.364
Hello?

38:28.891 --> 38:30.591
Hey, hey.

38:30.991 --> 38:31.991
Uh...

38:32.675 --> 38:34.601
I just wanted to let you know, um,

38:34.626 --> 38:36.786
I worked my situation out here. So...

38:37.583 --> 38:38.583
you don't need to worry.

38:41.972 --> 38:43.563
Okay. That's good.

38:43.588 --> 38:44.708
And, um...

38:45.424 --> 38:46.424
look, I'm...

38:47.523 --> 38:49.843
I'm sorry for what I said about...

38:50.622 --> 38:52.382
you coming over and looking me up.

38:53.260 --> 38:55.260
I know it's too late to
be your father, but...

38:56.413 --> 38:57.713
I'd like to be a friend.

39:02.280 --> 39:03.400
This is our dad.

39:04.420 --> 39:07.020
- Hey, man.
- So, this is how you got my back?

39:07.615 --> 39:09.415
- Hey, wait, son.
- Hey, now.

39:10.104 --> 39:11.504
I am not your son.

39:16.235 --> 39:18.455
Yeah, I could always use another friend.

39:21.595 --> 39:23.195
Okay, that's great.

